Nodes  (stores info of individual nodes)
------
node_id
node_type


Event_Conditions (stores info of the event conditions)
-------
event_id
condition_expression //ex-> age >= 25, event_type = 'checkout'
next_node_id


WorkflowNodeMapping (maps nodes to different workflows)
-------------
workflowmapping_id
workflow_id 
node_id

Workflow (stores info of the different workflows)
-------
worflow_id
workflow_name // ex->Order worflow, User workflow 
